係仲有啲白色嘅霧氣咁有啲blur／有啲眩光。<br />\n各位巴絲呢啲effect幾時會散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做smile試過失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55377a073645e64e6f16bd4856d0b0c8815356e8","tid":284903,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:31:28.000Z","msg":"點解唔問醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n術後果日應該有覆診架"},{"pid":"480c0297ecef6d11781387d81a341e0484aa6bfe","tid":284903,"uid":31896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:32:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔問醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n術後果日應該有覆診架</blockquote><br />\n有問佢呀，佢淨係話傷口埋得好靚，冇問題。啲嘢會慢慢散。<br />\n但隔離po嘅巴絲好似冇乜呢個問題咁"},{"pid":"8e6f8cc75e307c9db736f0e4e697073b0c43db26","tid":284903,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:34:12.000Z","msg":"我二月做<br />\n到今日望光源依然有眩光"},{"pid":"01569719d363dcd3dd8318297aaffb9fd9b5d6af","tid":284903,"uid":31896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我二月做<br />\n到今日望光源依然有眩光</blockquote><br />\n我越望得耐電腦就會越矇<br />\n訓醒嘅時候反而係最清楚"},{"pid":"2eb187e63dfc831d0594302fb31c6fdae7e18a9b","tid":284903,"uid":8812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:56:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我二月做<br />\n到今日望光源依然有眩光</blockquote><br />\n我越望得耐電腦就會越矇<br />\n訓醒嘅時候反而係最清楚</blockquote><br />\n聽完你講唔敢做了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咩當初唔簡lasik嘅？"},{"pid":"22e7c11347fee7d8065249ed15bcca819dc6f4f8","tid":284903,"uid":31896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我二月做<br />\n到今日望光源依然有眩光</blockquote><br />\n我越望得耐電腦就會越矇<br />\n訓醒嘅時候反而係最清楚</blockquote><br />\n聽完你講唔敢做了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咩當初唔簡lasik嘅？</blockquote><br />\n傷口細啲 又無咁invasive"},{"pid":"f2b1016a75553c4d667380f0ed430641482f406c","tid":284903,"uid":31896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我二月做<br />\n到今日望光源依然有眩光</blockquote><br />\n我越望得耐電腦就會越矇<br />\n訓醒嘅時候反而係最清楚</blockquote><br />\n聽完你講唔敢做了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咩當初唔簡lasik嘅？</blockquote><br />\n不過聽人講啲霧氣會1個星期無晒"},{"pid":"47eba2f0257ce358c70a42c16cc3af57c6ccbf6a","tid":284903,"uid":6163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T01:34:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我二月做<br />\n到今日望光源依然有眩光</blockquote><br />\n我越望得耐電腦就會越矇<br />\n訓醒嘅時候反而係最清楚</blockquote><br />\n聽完你講唔敢做了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咩當初唔簡lasik嘅？</blockquote><br />\n不過聽人講啲霧氣會1個星期無晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我星期二做 <br />\n星期四就無晒霧<br />\n不過左眼好似仲有近視定散光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為遮住一隻眼睇明顯係有分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe69081874d828e98cceca1ede28dd00cbe87bcf","tid":284903,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T01:42:51.000Z","msg":"點解啲醫生唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00ff09bbd1cecf49f1680e19129cc4c9836a7f6","tid":284903,"uid":28245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T01:47:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解啲醫生唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個問題其實好弱智 慘在你以為自己好醒"},{"pid":"e874d23bb0df9d8a7c5e95308b16cc72e7d2ce67","tid":284903,"uid":8827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T01:47:13.000Z","msg":"我2星期散哂"},{"pid":"bcd64e16e4a2ccf5bb89a92cfa20c25c3b3e44f8","tid":284903,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T01:51:59.000Z","msg":"<bl